<SYNC Start=674093><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=674229><P Class=KRCC>
책에서만 봤는데<br>그냥 관광객용 동굴이야
<SYNC Start=677218><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=677696><P Class=KRCC>
