<SYNC Start=722586><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=722729><P Class=KRCC>
그럭저럭
<SYNC Start=725251><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=725396><P Class=KRCC>
바빠서 자주 못 봐
<SYNC Start=728260><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=729229><P Class=KRCC>
