<SYNC Start=730559><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=732162><P Class=KRCC>
그게 뭐야!
<SYNC Start=734822><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=738596><P Class=KRCC>
