<SYNC Start=741960><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=751028><P Class=KRCC>
넌 남자 있어?
<SYNC Start=753688><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=753829><P Class=KRCC>
내겐 스포츠가 섹스야
<SYNC Start=755260><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=755396><P Class=KRCC>
엥?!
<SYNC Start=756692><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=756796><P Class=KRCC>
