<SYNC Start=765350><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=878529><P Class=KRCC>
깼어?
<SYNC Start=879586><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=880695><P Class=KRCC>
날샜어
<SYNC Start=881888><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=882028><P Class=KRCC>
좀 봐주라<br>5분만 더 잘게
<SYNC Start=885085><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=885229><P Class=KRCC>
