<SYNC Start=908087><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=908229><P Class=KRCC>
좋은 아침!
<SYNC Start=909388><P Class=KRCC>
&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=909462><P Class=KRCC>
